<HEADLINE>
BEST SELLERS: HARDCOVER BOOKS 
</HEADLINE>
   (For release on Sunday, Nov. 28)  
(Eds: This file is the full version of the best-seller list that
includes how many weeks each book has been on the list and where
the book stood the previous week. See BESTSELLERS-HARD-S-NYT for an
abbreviated format.) 
(lb) 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
