<HEADLINE>
THE HOURS THAT MAKE A STUDENT AN M.D. 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
(bl) 
 By ABIGAIL ZUGER, M.D.   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
