<HEADLINE>
FRENCH DIET SECRET: IF IT FEELS GOOD, EAT IT 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
(bl) 
 By ERIC NAGOURNEY   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
