<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-22 13:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7798 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a BC-SCI-AIDS-ART-BOS &LR;      11-22 1449
