it will buy 43 percent of Prodigy and make Prodigy its
Internet-access service for consumers and small businesses.
Financial terms were not disclosed Monday. SBC, the nation's
largest local telephone service company, will offer Prodigy's
service in markets covering about 100 million U.S. residents.
(Ladendorf, Austin American-Statesman)
