<P>
   CLINTON _ SOFIA, Bulgaria _ President Clinton, looking ahead to
his visit to Kosovo and Macedonia, today thanked Bulgaria for its
support during the 78-day NATO air war over Kosovo. The president
is scheduled to fly to the Yugoslav province _ and neighboring
Macedonia _ to express support for NATO and United Nations efforts
to build a peace between Serbs and ethnic Albanians. Developing.
(Deans, Cox News Service). 20.
</P>
<P>
   w/KINGSTON-CLINTON _ SOFIA, Bulgaria _ An interview with U.S.
Rep. Jack Kingston, R-Ga., who is traveling with President Clinton
on his tour of southern Europe. Developing. (Deans, Cox News
Service).
