<P>
   ANESTHESIA _ WASHINGTON _ The American Society of
Anesthesiologists called Monday for a congressional investigation
of a policy change under which specially trained nurses will be
given authority to administer anesthesia to patients at the
National Naval Medical Center in Bethesda, Md. This comes on the
heels of a Cox Newspapers story disclosing the new and
controversial practice. (Nesmith, Cox News Service). 20.
