<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-22 18:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8184 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u p BC-GORE-PROFILE-2TAKES-H     11-22 1429
