<P>
   CARE-ELDERLY (Los Angeles) -- Malnutrition, bedsores and
waste-tainted bath water were among the problems found at Los
Angeles County nursing homes during a recent congressional
investigation, according to a report released Monday. At a time
when America's aging population demands more long-term care, the
