   All the good parts just don't add up, though, to what the film
and we wish it was.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The film: &LR;  ``Flawless'' (R; language, violence, drug use). &UR;  &QL; 
The stars: &LR;  Robert De Niro, Philip Seymour Hoffman. &UR;  &QL; 
Behind the scenes: &LR;  Written and directed by Joel Schumacher.
Produced by Jane Rosenthal. Released by MGM. &UR;  &QL; 
Running time: &LR;  One hour, 50 minutes. &UR;  &QL; 
Playing: &LR;  Citywide &UR;  &QL; 
Our rating: &LR;  2.5 stars &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
