<P>
   (NYT15) DAVIS, Calif -- Nov. 22, 1999 -- SCI-MEREDITH-WINE,
11-22 -- Carole P. Meredith, at work in her California vineyard,
has shown that several well-known wine grapes are not pure strains
but hybrids, disconcerting those who thought hybrids inferior. ``I
think we are really on the threshold of understanding these
things,'' she says. (Peter DaSilva/New York Times Photo)
</P>
